name: VANISHED
description: In 1954, a mysterious man arrived at haneda airport in tokyo, japan. When questioned by custom officers, the mysterious passenger said he was from Taured, also referred to as Taured Mystery. To ensure that the mystery man didn’t escape, two guards were placed on the door. It must be mentioned that the hotel room in which he was staying only had one entry and exit point. But to everyone’s surprise, the man vanished the next morning. Not only that, but all his personal documents had also disappeared. A search was launched to find the man but in vain.
